  CheckCircle2, RefreshCw, Smartphone, Calendar, ShieldCheck,
  Cpu, Terminal, ShieldAlert, Network, Video, Palette, Image as ImageIcon,
  ChevronRight, Globe, Zap, ArrowRight, Shield
